# Plot the resulting raster of forest species richness
plot(rast(forest_spp_richness))

# Plot histograms of richness importance and rwr importance
hist(forest_spp_richness$richness_importance)

hist(forest_spp_richness$rwr_importance)

# Plot the relationship between richness importance and rwr importance
plot(forest_spp_richness$richness_importance, forest_spp_richness$rwr_importance)

# Plot the relationship between forest area and richness importance
plot(forest_spp_richness$area_forest, forest_spp_richness$richness_importance)

# Plot linear models of richness importance against other variables
forest_spp_richness |>
  pivot_longer(-c(x, y, rwr_importance, richness_importance)) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = value, y = richness_importance, color = name)) + 
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = TRUE) +
  theme_bw()
